theorem Topology.frontier_frontier_eq_frontier_diff_interior
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    frontier (frontier A) = frontier A \ interior (frontier A) := by
  have h : closure (frontier A) = frontier A :=
    Topology.closure_frontier_eq_frontier (A := A)
  simpa [frontier, h]

theorem Topology.interior_closure_interior_closure_interior_closure_interior_closure_interior_eq_interior_closure_interior
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior A)))))))) =
      interior (closure (interior A)) := by
  -- Define the operator `T := interior ∘ closure`.
  let T : Set X → Set X := fun S => interior (closure S)
  -- `T` is idempotent: `T (T S) = T S`.
  have h_idem : ∀ S : Set X, T (T S) = T S := by
    intro S
    dsimp [T]
    simpa using
      Topology.interior_closure_interior_closure_eq_interior_closure (A := S)
  -- Set `S0 = interior A`.
  let S0 : Set X := interior A
  -- The left-hand side is `T⁴ S0`.
  have h_lhs :
      interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior A)))))))) =
        T (T (T (T S0))) := by
    rfl
  -- Collapse the four iterates of `T` using idempotence.
  have h_collapse : T (T (T (T S0))) = T S0 := by
    calc
      T (T (T (T S0)))
          = T (T (T S0)) := h_idem (T (T S0))
      _ = T (T S0)       := h_idem (T S0)
      _ = T S0           := h_idem S0
  -- Replace the fourfold iterate with a single application of `T`.
  have h_final :
      interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior A)))))))) =
        T S0 := by
    simpa [h_collapse] using h_lhs
  -- Unfold `T` and `S0` to obtain the desired statement.
  simpa [T, S0] using h_final

theorem Topology.frontier_eq_closure_compl_of_dense {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} (hDense : closure A = (Set.univ : Set X)) :
    frontier A = closure (Aᶜ) := by
  calc
    frontier A = closure A ∩ closure (Aᶜ) := by
      simpa using
        (Topology.closure_inter_closure_compl_eq_frontier (X := X) (A := A)).symm
    _ = (Set.univ : Set X) ∩ closure (Aᶜ) := by
      simpa [hDense]
    _ = closure (Aᶜ) := by
      simp
